					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Usually people use cycle countdown timers which are decreased until the next "event" happens (such as the scanline changing, an interrupt firing, the PPU switching between backgrounds and sprites, etc..)
<br />You could also use Timestamp and Don't Exceed This Timestamp instead of a countdown.</div>

					
